# third-party skill installer destination (`.agents/`) — defensive ignore.
# The `postinstall: npx skills experimental_install -y` hook that auto-populated
# this directory was retired in mt#1902 (2026-05-19) after audit found zero
# consumers. The ignore is kept so any manual `npx skills` invocation or future
# third-party tooling that targets `.agents/` does not pollute the working tree.
# See docs/architecture/skills-surfaces.md for the `.agents/` vs `.minsky/skills/`
# distinction.
.agents/
.claude/worktrees/

# Per-session ephemeral artifacts (handoff notes, scratch files)
.minsky/sessions/

# Subagent dispatch artifacts — generated by session_generate_prompt and copied
# into the session for subagent reference; should never be committed
/.mt*-prompt.txt